1. left offset curve each road polygon's exterior ring
2. right offset curve each road polygon's interior ring
3. difference with ped polygons
4. explode
5. drop if not touching ped polygons
6. include curbs as pednet polygons for centerline computation
7. generate network
8. clip by curbs
9. RDP simplify each curb line
10. Mark all curb line points as False
11. Start at each curb line end where intersecting a true ped line of degree=2
12. Walk along points until >90 degree dtheta from sidewalk angle and mark as True
13. If any points for the simplified curb line, drop the polygon

14. generate centerlines from the remaining polygons

